2004-11-02  Drew Moseley  <drew.moseley@intel.com>

	* include/devs_eth_iq8033x.inl
	(CYGHWR_INTEL_I82544_PCI_VIRT_TO_BUS): Support 64-bit addressing
	for DMA buffers.
	(CYGHWR_INTEL_I82544_PCI_BUS_TO_VIRT): Ditto.

2004-06-09  Drew Moseley  <drew.moseley@intel.com>

	* cdl/iq8033x_eth_drivers.cdl: Provide a default EEPROM address bus
	width if the code is unable to determine it dynamically.

2003-11-10  Drew Moseley  <drew.moseley@intel.com>

	* cdl/iq8033x_eth_drivers.cdl: Assume an 82546 EEPROM bus width of
	6 bits.


2003-07-10  Drew Moseley  <drew.moseley@intel.com>

	* Initial IQ80331/IQ80332 CRB Platform Port

